<title>USA: ACT Networks stock repurchase program.</title>
<headline>ACT Networks stock repurchase program.</headline>
<dateline>CAMARILLO, Calif. 1997-08-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>ACT Networks Inc said on Friday  its board of directors approved a discretionary program to repurchase  up to $10 million worth of shares of the company's outstanding common  stock.</p>
<p>The purchases, subject to price and market conditions, will be made  from time to time in open market transactions using the company's  available cash balances.</p>
<p>ACT Networks develops, manufactures, and markets frame relay wide-area  network access products.</p>
